List of repositories for hab packages team:
* These are primary repositories where packages source code is hosted,  currently we are migrating packages from core-plans to core-packages and eventually core-plans will be archived.
  core-plans - https://github.com/habitat-sh/core-plans
  core-packages - https://github.com/habitat-sh/core-packages
  effortless - https://github.com/chef/effortless

* These are repositories for tools which help in Package Refresh at various stages during the course, collaborated with habitat core team
  hab-auto-build - https://github.com/habitat-sh/hab-auto-build
  release-monitor - https://github.com/habitat-sh/release-monitor
  build-order - https://github.com/habitat-sh/build-order

* These repositories are hosting documentations, discussions , how-to etc
  core-plan-dev - https://github.com/habitat-sh/core-plans-dev
  habitat-coreplan-refresher - https://github.com/habitat-sh/habitat-coreplan-refresher

* Apart from above, we have chef-base-plans (https://github.com/chef-base-plans) organisation which is now archived, used for commit history or changelogs
